  <brief_title>Skin Testing and ELISPOT Assay in Patients With a History of Non-Immediate Reactions to Cephalosporins</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Results of Skin Testing and The Detection of Cytokine Secretion From Drug Specific Peripheral Blood Mononuclear Cells Using ELISPOT Assay in the Diagnosis of Nonimmediate Reactions to Cephalosporins</official_title>
